column5: Looked out the back door and hour ago and there were 19 of them LOL
I could use one (never had wild) unless they commit suicide you won't touch them.  AND our hunter friends will be knocking at your door, go into lockdown quick.
Got a bunch here in a conservation area that walk right up to you folks feed them
Got enough of my own Lew, but thanks anyhow!
Nice pics lew !!! Lots over this way too as I have had to stop my truck & honk my horn to get them to move off the road before a few times !!!!!! Lol ....
They know when hunting season is...lol...I'll see them here everyday until the season opens, then not a one....until the day after the season ends....lol Maureen
